data.description: Welcome to your stunning haven in the highly sought-after Bentwater communityCowhere living meets luxury in a premier Golf, Swim, Tennis Community! Step into this lovingly cared-for home with gorgeous hardwoods that effortlessly complement the inviting 2-story family room, boasting a picturesque stone fireplace. Entertain in style with formal dining and living spaces, and enjoy leisurely mornings in the spacious kitchen with a delightful breakfast area overlooking a lush, wooded backyard. Upstairs holds three cozy bedrooms alongside a full bath, but the star of the show is the pristine oversized Master Suite with a spacious walk-in closet and a beautiful Master Bath featuring a double vanity, separate tile shower and garden tub. This home's got upgrades galore! BRAND NEW ROOF in 2020, HVAC systems less than 2 years old, fresh exterior paint summer of 2023, a charmingly landscaped back paver patio and retaining wall installed in 2021. Plus, new kitchen appliances from 2019 are sure to impress. But wait, there's more! The fully finished basement is a game-changerCoa versatile space for family fun or accommodating guests with a full bath boasting a roomy tile shower, plus separate flex space or guest bedroom
